Package: tarmander
Title: Easily Switch Between `targets` Scripts
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Luna", "Fazio", , "bmfazio@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Call `tarmander` to print the current active `targets` project.
    Call `tarmander()` to switch between projects. A project is a subfolder of the
    current directory which contains a `_targets.R` file.
